config-multi-provider-setup.value: Configured 13 providers: 3 direct (Anthropic, OpenAI, Gemini) + 10 via OpenRouter (Qwen, Mistral, Meta-Llama, DeepSeek, Z-AI, NVIDIA, X-AI, AllenAI, NousResearch, Arcee-AI). 202 total models across 4 tiers: free, cheap, moderate, premium. API keys stored in .bashrc environment variables, not hardcoded in config files.

pattern-openrouter-models.value: OpenRouter models must be explicitly listed in config.yaml under openrouter.models section. Free models end with :free suffix. Models organized by provider (qwen/, mistralai/, meta-llama/, etc.) and cost tier (free, cheap, moderate, premium).
